query:
SELECT sc.id as calendar_id, sc.name as calendar_name, sc.inviteCode, 
       cm.userId, cm.role, u.name as user_name,
       e.id as event_id, e.title as event_title, e.calendarId as event_calendarId
FROM shared_calendars sc
LEFT JOIN calendar_members cm ON sc.id = cm.calendarId
LEFT JOIN users u ON cm.userId = u.id
LEFT JOIN events e ON sc.id = e.calendarId
ORDER BY sc.id, cm.userId;
